                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-x-4">
                    <button class="px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-yellow-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-yellow-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-yellow-600">
                        Crea tu evento
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
